                immediately immediately upon passing through an RFID gantry or
                by physical inspection (handheld RFID readers). by physical
                inspection (handheld RFID readers).
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-6 fes7-text-cont">
              <h1
                class="section-title"
                style="border-left: white 2px solid; color: white"
              >
                HOW DOES
                <span class="bold" style="color: white"> RFID TECHNOLOGY</span>
                 WORK?
              </h1>

              <p style="color: white">
                RFID solutions include RFID antennas, RFID readers
