            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <img src="/images/precintos3rfid.png" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-section video-ads-bg">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="video-ads-text-cont clearfix">
            <span class="video-ads-text">RFID SEALS</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="app-glinseal" class="page-section p-80-cont">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8">
              <div class="mt-60 mb-40">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                  WHAT IS
                  <span class="bold">GLINSEAL</span>?
                </h2>
              </div>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-8">
                  <div class="fes7-box mb-20 wow fadeIn">
                    <div class="fes5-box wow fadeIn">
                      The Glinseal platform integrates a set of functional
                      modules for the management and administration of RFID
                      seals, including tamper detection and linkage with
                      transport units or containers.
                      <br />
                      <br />
                       Glinseal was designed to detect acts of vandalism or
                      tampering and cloning of RFID seals. Our system easily
                      integrates with X-ray scanners, intelligent gantry systems
                      (TOTEMS) and OCR systems, providing increased levels of
                      security while streamlining inspection processes.
                      <br />
                      <br />
                       We offer technological solutions that simplify the
                      implementation of security devices, with products and
                      services that add value to the areas of transportation,
                      security and logistics, improving monitoring, planning and
                      control processes.
                      <br />
                      <br />
                       Connectivity, real-time analysis and the use of robust
                      and efficient security mechanisms are the future of
                      international trade operations for a connected and agile
                      global economy.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 fes9-img-cont clearfix">
              <div class="fes9-img-center clearfix">
                <div class="fes9-img-center">
                  <Image
                    src={mockup1}
                    alt="foto"
                    class="wow fadeInUp"
                    data-wow-delay="450ms"
                    data-wow-duration="1s"
                    loading="lazy"
                  />

                  <Image
                    src={mockup2}
                    alt="foto"
                    class="wow fadeInUp"
                    data-wow-delay="450ms"
                    data-wow-duration="1s"
